name: ﾌ卂ᗪ乇  丂卩卂匚乇  ᗪ尺卂Ꮆㄖ几 🐉 🌌
description: I drew this radioactive ☢️ jade space dragon in virtual reality, in Google Tiltbrush. 💚 . . I used to draw a lot of horses as a child and studied their internal and external anatomy in great detail, which is why this reptile's musculature looks decidedly equine. 🤔 oops
